<% if current_user.role == 3 %>
<div class="help_accordion">
	<h3>Manage Students</h3>
		<div class="help_accordion">
			<h3>What do you do here?</h3>
				<div>
					<p>This is where you will add or edit any student.  You will also be able to create a new
						section of students.</p>
				</div>
			<h3>How do you add a student?</h3>
				<div>
					<p>Click on the link that says "Add Students," and you will directed to a page where you can
						enter a students information to be added to your section.</p>
				</div>
			<h3>What is the "Choose action" dropdown menu?</h3>
				<div>
					<p>Here you will be able to perform actions on students.</p>
					<p>These actions are:<br />
						1) Promote Student - Make that student a student manager.<br />
						2) Demote Student - Make that student manager a regular student again.<br />
						3) Add Team - Create a team of students to be under a student manager.</p>
					<p>To perform an action:<br />
						1) Select the student(s) by checking the checkbox next to their name.<br />
						2) Choose the action from the dropdown menu.<br />
						3) Click submit next to the dropdown and that's it
					</p>
				</div>
			<h3>What are the checkboxes used for?</h3>
				<div>
					<p>The checkboxes will be used in conjunction with the "Choose action" dropdown menu.  You 
						can choose the action from the dropdown menu and then use the checkboxes to select the 
						student(s) you want to perform the action on.  Once you have checked the student(s), 
						click the submit button next to the "Choose action" dropdwon menu.</p>
					<p>See What is the "Choose action" dropdown menu? to find out more about the available
						actions.</p>
				</div>
		</div>
	
	<h3>Assign Clients</h3>
	<div>
		<p></p>
	</div>
	
	<h3>Approve Clients</h3>
	<div>
		<p></p>
	</div>
	<h3>Reports</h3>
	<div>
		<p></p>
	</div>
	<h3>Navigation</h3>
		<div>
			<p>Here is our recommendation for navigating through Ad It:</p>
			<p>1) First and foremost, we do not recommend using the Back and Forward buttons on the web browser.<br />
				2) The navigation bar (Manage Students, Assign Clients, Approve Clients, Reports, and Help) is 
